<!-- About Start -->
<div class="container-xxl py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s" style="min-height: 400px;">
                <div class="position-relative h-100">
                    <img class="img-fluid position-absolute w-100 h-100" src="https://iqrais.paktaleem.org/local/aboutus/img/aboutcontent.jpg" alt="" style="object-fit: cover;">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
                <h1 class="section-title bg-white text-start text-primary pe-3 pb-2">About Us</h1>
                <h2 class="pb-2">
                    Welcome to PakTaleem Quran School
                </h2>
                <p class="pb-2">
                    Welcome to PakTaleem Quran School, a place where we strive to provide high-quality education of the Quran to students from all around the world.
                </p>
                <p class="pb-2">
                    Our academy was established with the goal of making the teachings of the Quran accessible to everyone, regardless of their location or background. We believe that the Quran is a source of guidance and wisdom for all humanity, and it is our mission to help individuals understand and apply its teachings in their daily lives.
                </p>
                <p class="pb-2">At PakTaleem Quran Academy, we have a team of experienced and knowledgeable teachers who are passionate about teaching the Quran. They are trained to use modern teaching techniques to ensure that our students have an engaging and effective learning experience.</p>
                <p class="pb-2"> <strong> We offer a variety of courses to meet the needs of our students, including Quran memorization, Quranic Arabic, tajweed (proper Quranic recitation), and Islamic studies. Our courses are tailored to students of all ages and levels, from beginners to advanced learners.</strong></p>
                
                <p class="pb-2">Thank you for considering PakTaleem Quran Academy as your partner in Quranic education. We look forward to helping you achieve your goals and reach your full potential as a student of the Quran.</p>
                <div class="row gy-2 gx-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="col-sm-6">
                        <p class="mb-0"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>Skilled Instructors</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-6">
                        <p class="mb-0"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>Online Classes</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-6">
                        <p class="mb-0"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>International Certificate</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-6">
                        <p class="mb-0"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>Satisfied Students</p>
                    </div>                    
                </div>               
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
